WorkItem.Description:
If I try to apply a paragraph style to a cell addText() call, the paragraph style is ignored.  When I update the Cell.php file such that the addText() function matches the Section.php addText() function, the paragraph style is honored:

        public function addText($text, $styleFont = null, $styleParagraph = null) {
                $text = utf8_encode($text);
                $text = new PHPWord_Section_Text($text, $styleFont, $styleParagraph);
                $this->_elementCollection[] = $text;
                return $text;
        }
